        "@value": "negative relative change of volume stem:[V] (<<iso80000-3>>) of an object\nunder pressure stem:[p] (<<t4-14.1>>) expressed by:\n\nstem:[kappa= -1/V (\"d\"V)/(\"d\"p)]\n",
